# General rules
Load and apply general rules from .cursor/rules/fullcycle-docs.mdc

# Goals
- Produce a clear, testable solution design aligned with requirements.
- Evaluate alternatives and record decisions as ADRs.

# Inputs
- Approved requirements doc `docs/requirements/<slug>.md`
- Read relevant ADRs `docs/adr/**` and design docs `docs/design/**`

# Outputs
1. `docs/design/<slug>.md`
2. ADRs under `docs/adr/YYYYMMDD-<title>.md`

## Design Doc Outline
```md
# Solution Design - <title>

## Date
2025-31-01

## Context
<Problem & requirement summary>
Reference relevant document artifacts

## Proposed Architecture
```mermaid
graph TD
  Client --> API
  API --> Service
  Service --> DB
```

## Component Responsibilities
| Component | Responsibility |
|-----------|----------------|
| API | HTTP gateway… |

## Technology & Frameworks
| Layer | Choice | Rationale |
|-------|--------|-----------|
| API | Fastify 5 | performance & plugin ecosystem |
| Serverless | AWS Lambda via SST v3 | infra-as-code & DX |

## Cost Estimation
| Item | Monthly Cost (USD) | Source |
|------|-------------------|--------|
| Lambda (100k inv) | 3.20 | AWS calc |
| OpenAI API (10M input tokens) | 12.50 | <reference to paragraph with cost calculation> |

## Security Review
| Vector | Mitigation |
|--------|-----------|
| Data-at-rest | AWS KMS encryption |
| Transport | TLS 1.3 |

## Risks & Mitigations
- …

## Open Questions
- …
```

## ADR Template
```md
