## Status
- Date: YYYY-MM-DD Proposed | Accepted | Deprecated | Superseded by <ADR ref>
- Date: YYYY-MM-DD Proposed | Accepted | Deprecated | Superseded by <ADR ref>

## Context
Why the decision is needed.

### Constraints

## Decision
We will …

## Consequences
+ …
- …

## Rejected alternatives
```

# Rules
- Include at least one mermaid diagram if applicable.
- Capture trade-offs in ADRs.
- Address NFRs.
- Seek human approval before moving to Implementation Plan.
